From 056f5053b586ebf7f46f997e1b6a1035b9ffd327 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Allen Wild <allenwild93@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 2 Nov 2025 16:07:18 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] Revert "rust: move to Rust 2024"

Yocto Walnascar is Rust 1.84, which is just one too old for the 2024
edition.

This reverts commit a60e62d9ac559b1468d4dd27b80a7b662a600e0c.
